- End-to-end test planning

## Code Example
```javascript
// watcher: rotate tenant certs and reload proxy
const fs = require('fs');
const { execSync } = require('child_process');
const watchDir = '/var/lib/proxy/certs';
const watcher = require('chokidar').watch(watchDir);
watcher.on('change', (path) => {
  if (path.endsWith('.pem')) {
    fs.copyFileSync(`${watchDir}/current.pem`, '/var/run/proxy/current.pem.bak');
    execSync('systemctl reload rhproxy');
  }
});
```

## Follow-up Questions
- How would you revoke a tenant cert without downtime?
- How would you validate multi-tenant isolation under load?

